程序包 com.example.catchthecode

类 modelUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.catchthecode.modelUser
  • public class modelUser
extends java.lang.Object
    The modelUser class is used to store the user's information including their ID, name, contact information, total score, and the list of codes that they have scanned. The class provides methods to get and set these attributes as well as to add and remove codes from the list and update the user's total score and number of scanned codes.
